s has banned ractopamine pork import</p></td><td class=\"w-min-12\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_8rxqgo9flsog-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">Info manipulation</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">❌ Not fact</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">🇨🇳 CCP state media participation</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"list-set bubbles w-min-16 ccp china other\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_8rxqgo9flsog-0\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200902000069-260407?chdtv\">Chiang Wan-an</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (蔣萬安)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/forum/20200904/74IKBMZM2ZA75PDOAPKVBYLLSI/\">Chao Shao-kang</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (趙少康)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1503745219913314_3033792466908574\">Sun Ta-chien</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (孫大千)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-11-03/660572\">Taiwan People’s Party</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12539/5868762\">Eric Chu</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (朱立倫)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/docDetail.jsp?id=100010539&amp;channel=2805\">HKCNA</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.uschinapress.com/static/content/SZ/2021-11-06/906499793072041984.html\">US China Press</a></span></li></ul></td><td class=\"w-min-16\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_33u0uq8if2e0-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c17\">Minister of COA </span><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12539/5909422\">Chen Chi-chun</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (陳吉仲)</span></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c8\">In addition, there are 2 government propaganda found in a relatively large quantity of Facebook posts. Readers should stay alert.</span></p><a id=\"t.b77f0e873fae596061c2248720c3b88c4724c46f\"></a><a id=\"t.2\"></a><div class=\"gdoc-table-container\"><div class=\"table\"><table class=\"c23\"><tbody><tr class=\"c9\"><th class=\"c11 w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c2\">Narratives</span></p></th><th class=\"c11 w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c2\">Features</span></p></th><th class=\"c11 list-set bubbles w-min-12 gov\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c2\">Supporting nodes</span></p><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_a98uv7a556zx-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c2\">TW gov</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">Other</span></li></ul></th><th class=\"c11 list-set bubbles w-min-12 kmt ccp\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c13\"><span class=\"c2\">Opposing nodes</span></p><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_sbgemf8bu3fc-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 kmt\"><span class=\"c2\">KMT</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c2\">CCP</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">Other</span></li></ul></th></tr><tr class=\"c9\"><td class=\"w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Banning ractopamine pork is banning American pork</p></td><td class=\"w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_dsa9i8kigop2-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">🇹🇼 Gov propaganda</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">✅ Status quo</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">⚠️ Oversimplification</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"list-set bubbles w-min-12 gov\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_dsa9i8kigop2-0\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/posts/10157750456266065\">Tsai Ing-wen</a></span></li></ul></td><td class=\"list-set bubbles w-min-12 kmt ccp\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_4gkzv2efdfe5-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 kmt\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12539/5868762\">Eric Chu</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (朱立倫)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 kmt\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20211117/2125703.htm\">Chiang Wan-an</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (蔣萬安)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 kmt\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.taiwanhot.net/news/979015/%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E8%90%8A%E8%B1%AC%E9%9D%9E%E5%8F%8D%E7%BE%8E%E8%B1%AC%E3%80%8D+%E6%9E%97%E7%82%BA%E6%B4%B2%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%83%B3%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E6%B7%B7%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%AB%87\">Lin Wei-chou</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (林為洲)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/4021759\">Ko Wen-je</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (柯文哲)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20211103005804-260407?chdtv\">Christina Yang</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (楊寶楨)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.taihainet.com/news/twnews/bilateral/2021-11-02/2567047.html\">Taihai</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.crntt.tw/doc/46_0_106214805_1_1102125616.html\">CRNTT.tw</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.crntt.tw/doc/46_0_106214805_1_1102125616.html\">CRNTT.tw</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.taiwan.cn/taiwan/jsxw/202111/t20211102_12388411.htm\">taiwan.cn</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.itaiwannews.cn/2021-11-03/ae8be523-2c53-89fe-e867-e280c07c6951.html\">iTaiwan News</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4 c12\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://taiwan.huanqiu.com/article/45aZkrRxh9z\">Huanqiu</a></span></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"c9\"><td class=\"w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Taiwan will be unable to join CPTPP if ractopamine pork import is banned</p></td><td class=\"w-min-8\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_5d9h2un5c0me-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">🇹🇼 Gov propaganda</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c2\">⚠️ Unfalsifiability</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"list-set bubbles w-min-12 gov\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_5d9h2un5c0me-0\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202110290267.aspx\">Su Tseng-chang</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (蘇貞昌)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12539/5856840\">Lai Ching-te</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (賴清德)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://wantrich.chinatimes.com/news/20211029900605-420501\">Wang Mei-hua</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (王美花)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 gov\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=95&amp;sms=73&amp;s=96725\">MOFA</a></span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12539/5901492\">Lee Chun</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (李淳)</span></li></ul></td><td class=\"list-set bubbles w-min-12 kmt ccp\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_vwtxwqnjdenf-0 start\"><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 kmt\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/202111020330.aspx\">Ling Tao</a></span><span class=\"c2\"> (凌濤)</span></li><li class=\"c6 li-bullet-0 ccp\"><span class=\"c4\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"http://www.taihainet.com/news/twnews/twdnsz/2021-10-29/2566212.html\">Taihai</a></span></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c8\">Based on the abovementioned 10 narratives, IORG has the following conclusions:</span></p><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_qan38nhgta8r-0 start\"><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">7 of the 8 information manipulation narratives are related to ractopamine pork, 1 is related to the protection of algal reefs and the Fourth Nuclear Power Plant. 2 government narratives also concern ractopamine pork.</span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Based on the limited number of cases, ractopamine pork is more likely to be a topic of information manipulation among the 4 referendum topics. IORG argues two reasons: (1) Ractopamine pork directly concerns Taiwan-U.S. relations, the CCP has strong incentives to influence and direct Taiwanese public opinion towards U.S. skepticism and hostility. (2) Food safety is a sensitive topic to the people of Taiwan. By promoting health concerns on ractopamine pork, the CCP can amplify people’s distrust towards the Taiwanese government.</span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">CCP participation can be found in all of the 10 narratives. Among the 10 narratives, 2 are initiated by the CCP: “Taiwanese pork products tested excessive ractopamine in Hongkong” and “Chinese state media quotes netizens to equate ractopamine pork with addictive drugs (“poisonous substance”)”.</span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">“Taiwan purchased American ractopamine pork and weapons, therefore it should receive American vaccines”, “Banning ractopamine pork is banning American pork” and “Taiwan will be unable to join CPTPP if ractopamine pork import is banned” have the most number of Facebook posts, far outnumbering other 7 narratives.</span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span>CCP quotes netizens to spread these 2 narratives in criticizing the Taiwanese government: “The ruling party imports ractopamine pork, selling out public health” and “Chinese state media quotes netizens to equate ractopamine pork with addictive drugs (“poisonous substance”)”. Similar situation has also been found in </span><span class=\"c18\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/da/10\">DA.10</a></span><span class=\"c8\">.</span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Despite clarifications from Taiwan’s Council of Agriculture (COA) and Mainland Affairs Council (MAC), the false narrative “Taiwanese pork products tested excessive ractopamine in Hongkong”, initiated by Chinese state media Wen Wei Po (文匯報) continues to spread among among LINE chat groups, and evolves into the narrative that “Taiwan’s ractopamine pork products are on sale in Hongkong, so ractopamine pork is also being sold in Taiwan”. The updated narrative implies that “Taiwan actually has ractopamine pork” and “the government is lying”.</span></li></ul><div class=\"separator\"></div><a id=\"t.ddc8da8f14956e0838fde572a21f3dff62665921\"></a><a id=\"t.3\"></a><div class=\"gdoc-photo-container\"><div class=\"images\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/AseVOmQmfZdK6U-A5FkOTdT37jPzUPIpGoL6nss2Q3fIu-m9A1wHXKW4-aQyey04xkN7SvT4M_5Qaefp9kDHlbUhgcnJbkt2VCNDxr5JpBT34TRjhQWkm3QxatwB7D8J7A\" title=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"separator\"></div><p class=\"c14\"><span>Full version of this Dokidoki Alert is available in Taiwanese Mandarin. Please visit </span><span class=\"c18\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/da/16\">https://iorg.tw/da/16</a></span><span class=\"c8\"> for more.</span></p><div class=\"separator\"></div><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c8\">Also…</span></p><ul class=\"c7 lst-kix_a52ds2ibcu8r-0 start\"><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c18\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/_en/open/research-method\">IORG Research Method</a></span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c18\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/_en/china-watch\">IORG China Watch</a></span></li><li class=\"c5 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c18\"><a class=\"c0\" href=\"https://iorg.tw/_en/da\">IORG Dokidoki Alert</a></span></li></ul>",
